'''Center for Political Technologies''' is one of the oldest independent think-tanks in [[Russia]]. Qualifications of the CPT team combine diverse areas and expertise, including politics, sociology, psychology, public relations, marketing, advertising, etc.

CPT has a permanent staff of 70 people working in 13 departments, led by Dr. [[Igor Bunin]]. It also attracts part-time experts "on project basis".

Client of the Center include a number of governmental organizations and NGOs, as well as a number of domestic and international commercial groups.[http://www.cpt.ru/english.php]

CPT also maintains a site of political commentaries [http://www.politcom.ru/ Politcom.Ru] (in Russian).

